{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"关于","page":{"layout":"document","title":"论文与研究","description":"eunomia-bpf 社区在 eBPF、用户态运行时、GPU systems 和 AI Agent infrastructure 方向发表的论文、预印本、artifact 与技术解读。","descriptionIsExcerpt":false,"bodyHtml":"<p>本页是 eunomia-bpf 社区研究成果的 canonical index，收录社区产出或直接相关的论文。每条记录包含论文、公开 artifact 和对应的技术 Blog。“待补 Blog”表示这项研究仍缺少面向开发者的独立解读。</p>\n<h2 id=\"2026\">2026</h2>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>论文</th><th>Artifact</th><th>技术 Blog</th><th>状态</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.02748\">Characterizing and Bridging the Diagnostic Gap in eBPF Verifier Rejections</a></td><td><a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/bpfix\">bpfix</a></td><td>待补 Blog</td><td>arXiv preprint</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.25189\">ActPlane: Programmable OS-Level Policy Enforcement for Agent Harnesses</a></td><td><a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/ActPlane\">ActPlane</a></td><td><a href=\"/zh/blog/2026/05/31/actplane-pushing-agent-harness-enforcement-down-to-kernel-ebpf/\">阅读 Blog</a></td><td>arXiv preprint，v2</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.24213\">Kops: Safely Extending the eBPF Compilation Pipeline with Native Operations</a></td><td><a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/bpf-benchmark\">Kops artifact</a></td><td>待补 Blog</td><td>arXiv preprint</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.20625\">ACRFence: Preventing Semantic Rollback Attacks in Agent Checkpoint-Restore</a></td><td>论文中描述的 artifact</td><td><a href=\"/zh/blog/2026/05/21/acrfence-preventing-semantic-rollback-attacks-in-agent-checkpoint-restore/\">阅读 Blog</a></td><td>arXiv preprint</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.11438\">NCCLbpf: Verified, Composable Policy Execution for GPU Collective Communication</a></td><td><a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/nccl-eBPF\">nccl-eBPF</a></td><td>待补 Blog</td><td>arXiv preprint</td></t