-extending-ebpf-from-kernel-to-user-space/\">bpftime 背景</a>，OSDI 论文解读待补</td><td>OSDI 2025</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"早期工作\">早期工作</h2>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>论文</th><th>Artifact</th><th>技术 Blog</th><th>状态</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.01837\">Code-Survey: An LLM-Driven Methodology for Analyzing Large-Scale Codebases</a></td><td><a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/code-survey\">code-survey</a></td><td><a href=\"/zh/blog/2024/10/01/can-llms-understand-linux-kernel-a-new-ai-powered-approach-to-understanding-large-codebases/\">阅读 Blog</a></td><td>arXiv preprint</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2408.04856\">Wasm-bpf: Streamlining eBPF Deployment in Cloud Environments with WebAssembly</a></td><td><a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/wasm-bpf\">wasm-bpf</a></td><td><a href=\"/zh/blog/2023/02/11/wasm-bpf-a-common-ebpf-kernel-programmability-for-cloud-native-webassembly/\">阅读 Blog</a></td><td>arXiv preprint</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2312.05531\">KEN: Kernel Extensions using Natural Language</a></td><td><a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/KEN\">KEN</a></td><td><a href=\"/zh/blog/2024/07/11/simplifying-kernel-programming-the-llm-powered-ebpf-tool/\">阅读 Blog</a></td><td>eBPF@SIGCOMM 2024</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"如何保持索引更新\">如何保持索引更新</h2>\n<p>仓库每周运行一次定时审计，把本页与近期 arXiv 记录比较，同时检查论文和 artifact 链接、中英文覆盖以及 Blog 状态。发现 drift 后，自动任务会创建或更新同一个 GitHub issue。Maintainer 在发布论文相关变更前，也可以手动运行同一项审计。</p>","headings":[{"id":"2026","text":"2026","depth":2},{"id":"2025","text":"2025","depth":2},{"id":"早期工作","text":"早期工作","depth":2},{"id":"如何保持索引更新","text":"如何保持索引更新","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/others/papers/README.zh.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2026-07-11T06:45:04.000Z","createdAt":"2026-07-11T06:45:04.000Z","authors":[{"name":"LinuxDev9002","email":"i@littlefisher.me"}]},"path":"